data.message: Don't post what you don't want people to see. The other day I was on my way our and turned on my GPS   and my WiFi and it showed an FBI van in nearby.?! Not that I have anything to hide. If it something I want to share with just one person then I message that person. Otherwise my life is open book can be check up on internet already. Will try not to offend any my fb friends and family. They don't have read every post, I'm sure that they don't and I won't post every little thing I do every second of the day. I do like some privacy. Enough said.
